title: ARE YOU TIRED OF PAYING RENT? BECOME A HOME OWNER
posting_body: Are you tired of paying your landlord's mortgage?
Now could be your time to invest in your future.
All you need is decent credit and a pre approval from a lender.
If you have questions about the pre approval process or are wondering if you qualify, I would be happy to get you some lender info to help start your journey.
Email me and lets find you a nice house!
If you are currently under an agreement with another real estate agent, please disregard this notice and information.
